    public class TypeWrapperDeserializer<T>
extends AbstractContainerDeserializer<T>
    Handler for a TypeWrapper type. Reads a class property first during deserialization and instantiates correct polymorphic type after. TODO ensuring class property will be first which is not the case for now!
